kieker.tools.logReplayer.filter

Class MonitoringRecordLoggerFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • kieker.analysis.analysisComponent.AbstractAnalysisComponent
      • kieker.analysis.plugin.AbstractPlugin
        • kieker.analysis.plugin.filter.AbstractFilterPlugin
          • kieker.tools.logReplayer.filter.MonitoringRecordLoggerFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAnalysisComponent, IFilterPlugin, IPlugin

    public class MonitoringRecordLoggerFilter
extends AbstractFilterPlugin
    Passes IMonitoringRecords received via its input port INPUT_PORT_NAME_RECORD to its own MonitoringController instance, which is created based on the Configuration file passed via the filter's property CONFIG_PROPERTY_NAME_MONITORING_PROPS_FN. Additionally, incoming records are relayed via the output port OUTPUT_PORT_NAME_RELAYED_EVENTS.
    Since:
    1.6
    Author:
    Andre van Hoorn
